#emph[Yes, Nitwik. Shouting would have alerted Boeb the Terrible. Yes, they made for very poor scouts. What was that? It would be dreadful for them if they got eaten by Boeb the Terrible? Aren't you full of original insights, Nitwik? That wasn't a compliment, but you're welcome nonetheless. Now, if you stopped interrupting me, you would know what happened next!]

#v(0.35em)
#line(length: 100%, stroke: rgb(90%, 90%, 90%))
