#emph[What happened to the friends? Well, Nitwik, they gathered their loot and went home, where they shared the loot with the rest of their swamp burrow. They celebrated Flib—who died foolishly, yes, but in service of something greater. And they basked in the experience and shared the tale of how they robbed Boeb of Boldwyr. Boeb the Terrible. There is a very clear lesson here. Can you tell me what it is? No, no! That is ] not#emph[ the lesson. Goodness, have I just wasted my entire afternoon? Don't laugh, Nitwik. I worry about you.]

#emph[Now, away with you. Away with you all! Auntie Grub has things to do.]
